column1: Daily Weather Observations for Armidale, New South Wales for March 2016
Prepared at 13:00 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW2004.201603
Most observations from the Armidale Tree Group Nursery site in Mann Street, but some from Armidale Airport.
